{
  "name": "Lowrider Candy",
  "description": "East-LA style candy lowrider. Deep candy apple base with candy cobalt panels, heavy gold leaf scrollwork, chrome trim all over, piano black roof, pearl fades, and a celtic-knot etched accent. Rolling sculpture.",
